TITLE: Getting ERC20 Token Metadata in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to fetch ERC20 token metadata using Moralis SDK in JavaScript. Requires Moralis API key and uses the EvmApi.token.getTokenMetadata endpoint to retrieve metadata for multiple token addresses on the Ethereum chain.
