TITLE: Configuring RainbowKit and Wagmi Providers in NextJS `_app.jsx` (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Configures RainbowKit and Wagmi in the main NextJS application component (`pages/_app.jsx`). It imports necessary modules, sets up chains (mainnet) and providers (publicProvider), initializes wagmi configuration (`createConfig`), and wraps the application components with `WagmiConfig`, `SessionProvider` (from next-auth), and `RainbowKitProvider` to make wallet connection and session management available throughout the app. Requires a WalletConnect `projectId` obtained from the WalletConnect Cloud dashboard.
