TITLE: Creating Moralis Stream for ENS Registrations in Python
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates creating a Moralis Stream using the Python SDK to monitor ENS 'NameRegistered' events. The script defines the event ABI, sets up advanced filtering options based on owner and cost (>1 ETH), configures stream parameters (webhook, description, tag, topic, chain ID), creates the stream, and adds the ENS Registry address. Requires the Moralis Python SDK (`pip install moralis`), a webhook URL, and an API key.
