TITLE: Initializing Moralis SDK and Creating a Stream in NodeJS
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet demonstrates how to initialize the Moralis SDK using an API key, define the parameters for a new stream (including target chains, description, tag, webhook URL, and whether to include native transactions), create the stream using `Moralis.Streams.add`, and then attach a specific wallet address to this newly created stream using `Moralis.Streams.addAddress`. It requires the `moralis` and `@moralisweb3/common-evm-utils` packages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/moralisweb3/docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.0/02-streams-api/evm/getting-started/using-node-js-sdk.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

