TITLE: Resolving ENS Domain using JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript implementation for resolving an ENS domain to an Ethereum address using Moralis API. Requires Moralis package and API key configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/moralisweb3/docs/blob/main/docs/01-web3-data-api/evm/wallet-api/07-Domains Lookups/how-to-resolve-ens-domain.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const Moralis = require("moralis").default;
const { EvmChain } = require("@moralisweb3/common-evm-utils");

const runApp = async () => {
  await Moralis.start({
    apiKey: "YOUR_API_KEY",
    // ...and any other configuration
