TITLE: Complete getWalletNfts Lambda Function Code (NodeJS)
DESCRIPTION: The complete JavaScript code for the `getWalletNfts.js` Lambda function. It requires and initializes the Moralis SDK, then defines the handler function which calls `Moralis.EvmApi.nft.getWalletNFTs` using `address` and `chain` from the event parameters (with a limit of 10) and returns the stringified NFT data.
