TITLE: Reporting Spam NFT Contracts with Moralis in Python
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to report spam NFT contracts using the Moralis API in Python. It uses the evm_api module from the moralis package to call the review_contracts endpoint with the necessary parameters and body to report a contract as spam.
SOURCE: https://github.com/moralisweb3/docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.0/01-web3-data-api/evm/nft-api/spam-detection/report-nft-spam.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
from moralis import evm_api

api_key = "YOUR_API_KEY"

body = {
    "contracts": [
        {
            "contract_address": "0x06012c8cf97bead5deae237070f9587f8e7a266d",
            "reason": "My Reason",
            "report_type": "spam",
            "contract_type": "NFT"
        }
    ]
}

params = {
    "chain": "eth"
}

result = evm_api.utils.review_contracts(
    api_key=api_key,
    params=params,
    body=body
)

print(result)
```

