SOURCE: https://github.com/moralisweb3/docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.0/01-web3-data-api/evm/token-api/05-Pairs & Liquidity/how-to-get-sushiswap-v2-pair-address.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

