DESCRIPTION: This JSON code defines a filter object for Moralis Streams, specifically targeting the `value` parameter of an event (like an ERC20 Transfer). It uses the `and` operator to combine two conditions: `gt` (greater than `5000000000`) and `lt` (less than `50000000000`). This effectively filters for events where the `value` is between 5000 and 50000 USDC (assuming 6 decimals), excluding the boundaries.
