SOURCE: https://github.com/moralisweb3/docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.0/01-web3-data-api/evm/token-api/04-Transfers/how-to-get-all-erc20-transactions-by-wallet.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
from moralis import evm_api

api_key = "YOUR_API_KEY"
params = {
    "address": "0x2260fac5e5542a773aa44fbcfedf7c193bc2c599",
    "chain": "eth"
}

result = evm_api.token.get_wallet_token_transfers(
    api_key=api_key,
    params=params,
)

print(result)
```

