TITLE: Querying NFT Trades by Contract Address using Moralis SDK in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to use the Moralis SDK to fetch NFT trade data for a specific contract address. It includes parameters for pagination and filtering by marketplace.
SOURCE: https://github.com/moralisweb3/docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.0/01-web3-data-api/evm/reference/10-NFT API/06-Get NFT Market Data/get-nft-trades.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import Moralis from 'moralis';
try {
    await Moralis.start({
        apiKey: "YOUR_API_KEY"
    });

    const response = await Moralis.EvmApi.nft.getNFTTrades({
        address: "0xbc4ca0eda7647a8ab7c2061c2e118a18a936f13d",
        chain: "0x1",
        fromBlock: 0,
        toBlock: 999999999,
        fromDate: "",
        toDate: "",
        limit: 100,
        cursor: "",
        marketplace: "opensea"
    });

    console.log(response.raw);
} catch (e) {
    console.error(e);
}
```

